   <p>See <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-05-02-0193" class="document">Jacob Hite to GW, 29 June</a>, <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-05-02-0197" class="document">John Hite to GW, 2 July 1758</a>, and notes.</p>

</div>
